message.content: cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.LG. The paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to identify the veracity of rumours and reactions to them in text. This falls under the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information retrieval (cs.IR), social and information networks (cs.SI), and machine learning (cs.LG).
